CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 22, 1959, pg. A10 reads: " "And One For You" says Dr. James Henry as he pours champagne into his son's glass at the 25th anniversary surprise reception given Saturday night. Daughter Jeanine, far left, son James Jr. and Lois Simms, second from right, planned the surprise for the Henrys, shown in center. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Double exposure: Dr. James F. Henry and Jerrie Henry cutting 25th anniversary cake in home on Cherokee Street; Portrait of Jerrie Henry surrounded by gifts in her home on Cherokee Street for 25th wedding anniversary
